128
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,480
It's scary.

129
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,000
Paddle! Paddle!

130
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:24,760
The result of his practise
beforehand doesn't help at all.

131
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:25,800
I see.

132
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:27,000
But it's impressive.

133
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,520
He runs out of strength at once.

134
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,600
I'm exhausted!

135
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,920
It was only four times.

136
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:36,920
He can't even return
to his starting place.

137
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,000
It comes again!

138
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:44,040
Like seaweed floating between waves.

139
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,720
Stop the waves!

140
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,600
As a result...

141
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:51,440
