183
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,640
Wow!

184
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:55,680
On the other hand,
Nakaoka doesn't go forward at all.

185
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,160
And then...

186
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,240
Wow, this is impressive!

187
