Hey! Darn it!

188
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,560
Nakaoka is defeated miserably.

189
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:06,080
It's totally different!

190
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:08,400
She isn't short of breath at all.

191
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:12,960
