on a rocking surfboard?

194
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:22,960
Do your best.

195
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:25,040
Okay...

196
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,600
Be still...

197
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,160
Be still... I'll stand.

198
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,160
No!

199
00:08:35,160 --> 00:08:37,800
