200
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:40,880
It's harder than taking
a tube surfing photo.

201
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,400
I think I won't fall.

202
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:44,800
- I think it's okay.
- I see, that's your goal?

203
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,480
