204
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:49,120
You can do it.

205
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:50,600
Okay.

206
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,800
Okay...

207
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:53,880
Her body is...

208
