213
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,480
You want to try again?

214
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:08,080
That's the vitality that endeavours
on a global scale.

215
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,320
Oh no...

216
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:12,400
