herself to this stupid trick.

219
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:21,400
Good... You can do it. Good...

220
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:25,360
You're standing...
Oh! You're standing! Impressive!

221
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,280
